      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, we have a situation. The candidate just pivoted on the Tax Act stance during the closed-door meeting, and if the press gets wind that we've completely reversed course since last month, our consistency scores are gonna tank. How should we handle the reporter who's definitely gonna ask why the position changed so suddenly?",
